---
import Icon from './MockIcon.astro';

const tabs = [
	{
		key: 'general',
		label: 'General',
		icon: 'settings',
	},
	{
		key: 'derivacion',
		label: 'Derivacion',
		icon: 'users',
	},
	{
		key: 'instrucciones',
		label: 'Instrucciones',
		icon: 'brain',
	},
	{
		key: 'recontactos',
		label: 'Recontactos',
		icon: 'refresh',
	},
];
---

<div class="ai-demo" data-agent-mock aria-label="Configuracion del agente IA con vista previa de WhatsApp" role="img">
	<div class="ai-app">
		<section class="ai-panel">
			<nav class="ai-tabs" aria-label="Configuracion del agente">
				{tabs.map((tab, index) => (
					<button class={index === 0 ? 'ai-tab is-active' : 'ai-tab'} type="button" data-agent-tab data-index={index}>
						<Icon name={tab.icon} />
						<span>{tab.label}</span>
					</button>
				))}
			</nav>

			<div class="ai-panel-body">
				<section class="ai-view is-active" data-agent-view>
					<div class="ai-head-row">
						<div class="ai-head">
							<span class="ai-icon-box"><Icon name="brain" /></span>
							<span>
								<strong>Agente WhatsApp IA</strong>
								<small>Configura el asistente de inteligencia artificial</small>
							</span>
						</div>
						<span class="ai-active">Activo <span class="ai-toggle is-on"></span></span>
					</div>

					<h4>Permisos del agente</h4>
					<div class="ai-perms">
						<div class="ai-perm">
							<div class="ai-perm-head"><span><Icon name="message" />Responder</span><span class="ai-toggle ai-toggle--sm is-on"></span></div>
							<p>El agente puede enviar mensajes</p>
						</div>
						<div class="ai-perm">
							<div class="ai-perm-head"><span><Icon name="tag" />Etiquetar</span><span class="ai-toggle ai-toggle--sm is-on"></span></div>
							<p>Aplica etiquetas a conversaciones</p>
						</div>
						<div class="ai-perm">
							<div class="ai-perm-head"><span><Icon name="pipeline" />Asignar etapa</span><span class="ai-toggle ai-toggle--sm is-on"></span></div>
							<p>Mueve leads en el pipeline</p>
						</div>
					</div>

					<h4>Coexistencia con WhatsApp Business</h4>
					<p class="ai-muted">Configura como se comporta la IA cuando un agente humano responde desde la app de WhatsApp Business.</p>
					<div class="ai-coex">
						<span>
							<strong>Pausar agente automaticamente</strong>
							<small>Al responder desde WhatsApp Business, la IA se pausa automaticamente en esa conversacion.</small>
						</span>
						<span class="ai-toggle is-on"></span>
					</div>
				</section>

				<section class="ai-view" data-agent-view>
					<div class="ai-head">
						<span class="ai-icon-box"><Icon name="users" /></span>
						<span>
							<strong>Derivacion</strong>
							<small>Como se reparten los leads entre tu equipo</small>
						</span>
					</div>

					<div class="ai-notice">
						<Icon name="alert" />
						<span>Por defecto la derivacion es automatica al agente asignado a la propiedad.</span>
					</div>

					<h4>Como se asignan?</h4>
					<p class="ai-muted">Cuando no hay una propiedad que defina el destino:</p>
					<div class="ai-choice-grid">
						<div class="ai-choice">
							<span class="ai-choice-icon"><Icon name="rotate" /></span>
							<strong>Equitativo</strong>
							<p>Uno por uno, en ronda. Todos los agentes reciben la misma cantidad de leads.</p>
							<small><Icon name="info" /> Por defecto</small>
						</div>
						<div class="ai-choice">
							<span class="ai-choice-icon"><Icon name="pie" /></span>
							<strong>Porcentajes</strong>
							<p>Vos definis que porcentaje de leads recibe cada agente.</p>
							<small><Icon name="sliders" /> Requiere configuracion</small>
						</div>
					</div>

					<div class="ai-summary">
						<strong><Icon name="eye" /> Resumen</strong>
						<p><b>Equitativo:</b> un lead para cada agente, por turnos. Todos participan por igual.</p>
					</div>
				</section>

				<section class="ai-view" data-agent-view>
					<label class="ai-label">Nombre del agente</label>
					<div class="ai-input">Jose</div>
					<p class="ai-muted">Asi se presentara ante tus clientes cuando le pregunten su nombre. Probalo en el playground.</p>

					<div class="ai-split-head">
						<h4>Instrucciones</h4>
						<span class="ai-segment"><b>Basico</b><span>Avanzado</span></span>
					</div>

					<div class="ai-instructions">
						<nav class="ai-submenu" aria-label="Tipos de instrucciones">
							<span class="is-on"><Icon name="sliders" />Tono y reglas</span>
							<span><Icon name="pin" />Alcance comercial <b>4</b></span>
							<span><Icon name="ban" />Que nunca hacer</span>
							<span><Icon name="calendar" />Datos y politicas <b>1</b></span>
							<span><Icon name="target" />Estilo de cierre</span>
						</nav>
						<div class="ai-config-card">
							<div class="ai-head ai-head--sm">
								<span class="ai-icon-box"><Icon name="sliders" /></span>
								<span>
									<strong>Tono y reglas de negocio</strong>
									<small>La personalidad del agente y las instrucciones propias que debe respetar.</small>
								</span>
							</div>
							<div class="ai-field-grid">
								<span><b>Tono</b><em>Profesional <Icon name="chevron" /></em></span>
								<span><b>Personalidad</b><em>Asistente proactivo <Icon name="chevron" /></em></span>
							</div>
							<label class="ai-label">Reglas de negocio</label>
							<div class="ai-textarea">No mencionar precios hasta que el cliente los solicite. Solo atender consultas de propiedades activas.</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</section>

				<section class="ai-view" data-agent-view>
					<div class="ai-head-row">
						<div class="ai-head">
							<span class="ai-icon-box"><Icon name="refresh" /></span>
							<span>
								<strong>Recontactos automaticos</strong>
								<small>Reintenta contactar leads que dejaron de responder</small>
							</span>
						</div>
						<span class="ai-active">Activo <span class="ai-toggle is-on"></span></span>
					</div>

					<div class="ai-split-head">
						<h4>Mensajes de recontacto</h4>
						<span class="ai-counter">2 de 3</span>
					</div>

					<div class="ai-recontact">
						<div class="ai-recontact-head">
							<strong><span>1</span> Recontacto 1</strong>
							<small>Esperar <b>1h</b></small>
						</div>
						<span class="ai-mode"><b><Icon name="brain" />Generado por IA</b><span><Icon name="edit" />Mensaje fijo</span></span>
						<label class="ai-label">Instruccion para la IA</label>
						<div class="ai-input">Manda un calido saludo para reactivar</div>
					</div>

					<div class="ai-recontact">
						<div class="ai-recontact-head">
							<strong><span>2</span> Recontacto 2</strong>
							<small>Esperar <b>2h</b></small>
						</div>
						<span class="ai-mode"><span><Icon name="brain" />Generado por IA</span><b><Icon name="edit" />Mensaje fijo</b></span>
						<label class="ai-label">Mensaje a enviar</label>
						<div class="ai-input">No te quiero molestar, pero me quede pensando en lo que me pediste.</div>
					</div>
				</section>
			</div>

			<div class="ai-actionbar">
				<button type="button">Cancelar</button>
				<button class="is-save" type="button" data-agent-save>Guardar cambios</button>
			</div>
		</section>

		<aside class="ai-wa" aria-label="Simulacion del agente IA en vivo">
			<header>
				<span class="ai-wa-avatar"><Icon name="brain" /><i></i></span>
				<span><strong>Jose</strong><small>en linea</small></span>
				<span class="ai-wa-actions"><Icon name="trash" /><Icon name="chevron-right" /></span>
			</header>
			<div class="ai-wa-body">
				<span class="ai-wa-day">HOY</span>
				<p><Icon name="lock" />Simulacion con la configuracion actual, incluso sin guardar. Ningun cliente real recibe estos mensajes.</p>
			</div>
			<footer>
				<span>Escribi un mensaje</span>
				<button type="button" aria-label="Enviar mensaje"><Icon name="send" /></button>
			</footer>
		</aside>
	</div>

	<div class="ai-progress" aria-hidden="true">
		{tabs.map((_, index) => <span class={index === 0 ? 'is-on' : ''} data-agent-dot></span>)}
	</div>
</div>

<script>
	const clamp = (value, min, max) => Math.min(max, Math.max(min, value));

	document.querySelectorAll('[data-agent-mock]').forEach((root) => {
		const tabs = Array.from(root.querySelectorAll('[data-agent-tab]'));
		const views = Array.from(root.querySelectorAll('[data-agent-view]'));
		const dots = Array.from(root.querySelectorAll('[data-agent-dot]'));
		const saveButton = root.querySelector('[data-agent-save]');
		const shell = root.closest('[data-agent-scroll-shell]');
		let current = -1;
		let frame = 0;

		const setActive = (index) => {
			if (index === current) return;
			current = index;
			tabs.forEach((tab, tabIndex) => tab.classList.toggle('is-active', tabIndex === index));
			views.forEach((view, viewIndex) => view.classList.toggle('is-active', viewIndex === index));
			dots.forEach((dot, dotIndex) => dot.classList.toggle('is-on', dotIndex === index));
			saveButton?.classList.toggle('is-disabled', !(index === 1 || index === 3));
		};

		const card = root.closest('.product-card--agent');

		// Distancia real en la que la card queda pinneada: del momento en que
		// llega a su 'top' sticky hasta que el shell termina de pasar.
		const getMetrics = () => {
			if (!(shell instanceof HTMLElement) || !(card instanceof HTMLElement)) return null;
			const cardTop = parseFloat(getComputedStyle(card).top) || 0;
			const pinned = Math.max(1, shell.offsetHeight - card.offsetHeight);
			return { cardTop, pinned };
		};

		const syncFromScroll = () => {
			frame = 0;
			if (tabs.length === 0 || window.innerWidth < 861) return;

			const metrics = getMetrics();
			if (!metrics || !(shell instanceof HTMLElement)) return;

			const rect = shell.getBoundingClientRect();
			const progress = clamp((metrics.cardTop - rect.top) / metrics.pinned, 0, 0.999);
			setActive(Math.floor(progress * tabs.length));
		};

		const requestSync = () => {
			if (frame) return;
			frame = window.requestAnimationFrame(syncFromScroll);
		};

		tabs.forEach((tab, index) => {
			tab.addEventListener('click', () => {
				const metrics = getMetrics();
				if (metrics && window.innerWidth >= 861 && shell instanceof HTMLElement) {
					const shellTop = shell.getBoundingClientRect().top + window.scrollY;
					const target = shellTop - metrics.cardTop + metrics.pinned * ((index + 0.5) / tabs.length);
					window.scrollTo({ top: target, behavior: 'smooth' });
					return;
				}
				setActive(index);
			});
		});

		const fitDemo = () => {
			if (!(root instanceof HTMLElement)) return;
			const card = root.closest('.product-card--agent');

			// Solo escalamos en el layout de escritorio (card pinneada).
			if (!(card instanceof HTMLElement) || window.innerWidth < 861) {
				root.style.transform = '';
				root.style.height = '';
				return;
			}

			root.style.transform = 'none';
			root.style.height = 'auto';

			const natural = root.scrollHeight;
			const cardStyles = getComputedStyle(card);
			const padBottom = parseFloat(cardStyles.paddingBottom) || 0;
			const available = card.getBoundingClientRect().bottom - padBottom - root.getBoundingClientRect().top;
			const scale = clamp(available / natural, 0.78, 1);

			root.style.transform = `scale(${scale})`;
			root.style.height = `${natural * scale}px`;
		};

		setActive(0);
		syncFromScroll();
		fitDemo();
		window.addEventListener('scroll', requestSync, { passive: true });
		window.addEventListener('resize', () => {
			requestSync();
			fitDemo();
		});
		window.addEventListener('load', fitDemo);
	});
</script>

<style>
	.ai-demo {
		position: relative;
		width: 100%;
		height: 100%;
		min-height: clamp(500px, 56vh, 620px);
		color: #1f2530;
		font-size: 14px;
		line-height: 1.45;
	}

	.ai-demo svg {
		display: block;
		width: 1em;
		height: 1em;
		fill: none;
		stroke: currentColor;
		stroke-width: 2;
		stroke-linecap: round;
		stroke-linejoin: round;
	}

	.ai-app {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr) minmax(300px, 360px);
		gap: 18px;
		height: 100%;
		min-height: 0;
	}

	.ai-panel,
	.ai-wa {
		min-width: 0;
		border: 1px solid #e8eaee;
		border-radius: 18px;
		background: #fff;
		box-shadow: 0 1px 2px rgba(16, 24, 40, 0.04), 0 20px 52px rgba(16, 24, 40, 0.08);
	}

	.ai-panel {
		position: relative;
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		overflow: hidden;
	}

	.ai-tabs {
		display: flex;
		gap: clamp(12px, 2vw, 26px);
		padding: 18px 24px 0;
		border-bottom: 1px solid #e8eaee;
		overflow-x: auto;
		scrollbar-width: none;
	}

	.ai-tabs::-webkit-scrollbar {
		display: none;
	}

	.ai-tab {
		display: inline-flex;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 8px;
		min-height: 42px;
		padding: 0 0 14px;
		border: 0;
		border-bottom: 2px solid transparent;
		background: transparent;
		color: #8a909b;
		font: inherit;
		font-weight: 700;
		white-space: nowrap;
		cursor: pointer;
		transition:
			color 220ms ease,
			border-color 220ms ease;
	}

	.ai-tab svg {
		width: 18px;
		height: 18px;
	}

	.ai-tab.is-active {
		border-color: #4e8c6f;
		color: #1f2530;
	}

	.ai-panel-body {
		position: relative;
		display: grid;
		flex: 1;
		min-height: 0;
	}

	.ai-view {
		grid-area: 1 / 1;
		padding: 26px 28px 86px;
		opacity: 0;
		pointer-events: none;
		transform: translateY(14px);
		transition:
			opacity 340ms ease,
			transform 340ms ease;
	}

	.ai-view.is-active {
		opacity: 1;
		pointer-events: auto;
		transform: translateY(0);
	}

	.ai-head-row,
	.ai-split-head {
		display: flex;
		align-items: flex-start;
		justify-content: space-between;
		gap: 18px;
	}

	.ai-head {
		display: flex;
		align-items: flex-start;
		gap: 13px;
		min-width: 0;
	}

	.ai-head strong {
		display: block;
		color: #1f2530;
		font-size: 1.18rem;
		line-height: 1.2;
	}

	.ai-head small {
		display: block;
		margin-top: 4px;
		color: #8a909b;
		font-size: 0.88rem;
	}

	.ai-head--sm strong {
		font-size: 1rem;
	}

	.ai-icon-box,
	.ai-choice-icon {
		display: grid;
		place-items: center;
		flex: 0 0 auto;
		width: 46px;
		height: 46px;
		border-radius: 12px;
		background: #eef5f1;
		color: #4e8c6f;
	}

	.ai-icon-box svg,
	.ai-choice-icon svg {
		width: 23px;
		height: 23px;
	}

	.ai-active {
		display: inline-flex;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 10px;
		color: #8a909b;
		font-weight: 700;
		white-space: nowrap;
	}

	.ai-toggle {
		position: relative;
		display: inline-block;
		flex: 0 0 auto;
		width: 44px;
		height: 25px;
		border-radius: 999px;
		background: #d6dadf;
	}

	.ai-toggle::after {
		content: '';
		position: absolute;
		top: 3px;
		left: 3px;
		width: 19px;
		height: 19px;
		border-radius: 50%;
		background: #fff;
		box-shadow: 0 1px 2px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.22);
	}

	.ai-toggle.is-on {
		background: #5b9d7f;
	}

	.ai-toggle.is-on::after {
		left: 22px;
	}

	.ai-toggle--sm {
		width: 35px;
		height: 20px;
	}

	.ai-toggle--sm::after {
		width: 14px;
		height: 14px;
	}

	.ai-toggle--sm.is-on::after {
		left: 18px;
	}

	.ai-view h4 {
		margin: 28px 0 13px;
		color: #1f2530;
		font-size: 1rem;
	}

	.ai-muted {
		margin: 8px 0 0;
		color: #8a909b;
		font-size: 0.88rem;
		line-height: 1.55;
	}

	.ai-perms,
	.ai-choice-grid,
	.ai-field-grid {
		display: grid;
		gap: 14px;
	}

	.ai-perms {
		grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
	}

	.ai-perm,
	.ai-coex,
	.ai-summary,
	.ai-recontact {
		border: 1px solid rgba(37, 154, 114, 0.18);
		border-radius: 14px;
		background: #f7fbf9;
	}

	.ai-perm {
		padding: 16px;
	}

	.ai-perm-head,
	.ai-perm-head span,
	.ai-summary strong,
	.ai-choice small,
	.ai-mode,
	.ai-mode span,
	.ai-mode b {
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 8px;
	}

	.ai-perm-head {
		justify-content: space-between;
		color: #1f2530;
		font-weight: 800;
	}

	.ai-perm-head svg {
		color: #4e8c6f;
	}

	.ai-perm p,
	.ai-coex small,
	.ai-choice p,
	.ai-summary p {
		margin: 12px 0 0;
		color: #8a909b;
		font-size: 0.82rem;
		line-height: 1.5;
	}

	.ai-coex {
		display: flex;
		align-items: flex-start;
		justify-content: space-between;
		gap: 18px;
		margin-top: 13px;
		padding: 18px;
	}

	.ai-coex strong {
		display: block;
	}

	.ai-notice {
		display: flex;
		gap: 11px;
		margin-top: 22px;
		padding: 14px 16px;
		border: 1px solid #f5ecca;
		border-radius: 12px;
		background: #fdf6e3;
		color: #7a6418;
	}

	.ai-notice svg {
		flex: 0 0 auto;
		width: 19px;
		height: 19px;
		color: #c79a2a;
	}

	.ai-choice-grid,
	.ai-field-grid {
		grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
	}

	.ai-choice {
		padding: 20px;
		border: 1px solid #e8eaee;
		border-radius: 14px;
		background: #f7f8fa;
	}

	.ai-choice strong {
		display: block;
		margin-top: 14px;
		font-size: 1.05rem;
	}

	.ai-choice small {
		margin-top: 16px;
		color: #a6abb4;
		font-weight: 700;
	}

	.ai-summary {
		margin-top: 18px;
		padding: 17px 18px;
		background: #f7f8fa;
		border-color: #e8eaee;
	}

	.ai-label {
		display: block;
		margin: 18px 0 9px;
		color: #1f2530;
		font-weight: 800;
	}

	.ai-input,
	.ai-textarea,
	.ai-field-grid em {
		border: 1px solid #dfe2e7;
		border-radius: 12px;
		background: #fff;
		color: #1f2530;
		font-style: normal;
	}

	.ai-input,
	.ai-textarea {
		padding: 13px 15px;
	}

	.ai-split-head {
		align-items: center;
		margin-top: 24px;
	}

	.ai-split-head h4 {
		margin: 0;
	}

	.ai-segment,
	.ai-mode {
		display: inline-flex;
		padding: 4px;
		border-radius: 10px;
		background: #eef0f3;
	}

	.ai-segment span,
	.ai-segment b,
	.ai-mode span,
	.ai-mode b {
		padding: 8px 14px;
		border-radius: 8px;
		color: #8a909b;
		font-size: 0.86rem;
		font-weight: 800;
	}

	.ai-segment b,
	.ai-mode b {
		background: #fff;
		color: #1f2530;
		box-shadow: 0 1px 2px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
	}

	.ai-instructions {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: minmax(190px, 0.42fr) minmax(0, 1fr);
		gap: 20px;
		margin-top: 18px;
	}

	.ai-submenu {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 4px;
	}

	.ai-submenu span {
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 10px;
		padding: 12px;
		border-radius: 12px;
		color: #6b7280;
		font-weight: 800;
	}

	.ai-submenu span.is-on {
		background: #eef5f1;
		color: #4e8c6f;
	}

	.ai-submenu b {
		margin-left: auto;
		padding: 2px 8px;
		border-radius: 8px;
		background: #eef0f3;
		color: #6b7280;
		font-size: 0.75rem;
	}

	.ai-config-card {
		min-width: 0;
	}

	.ai-field-grid {
		margin-top: 18px;
	}

	.ai-field-grid span {
		display: grid;
		gap: 8px;
	}

	.ai-field-grid em {
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: space-between;
		padding: 12px 14px;
